# Tauri's Rust-side dev watcher should ignore the frontend dirs — Vite owns
# their HMR. Critically, main.rs re-exports ui/src/bindings.ts on every debug
# startup (#[cfg(debug_assertions)]); without this ignore the watcher sees that
# write, restarts the app, which re-exports, looping forever. The gen-bindings
# bin + CI `git diff` gate (D-07) is the real freshness guarantee, not the
# watcher.
ui/
ui-react/
ui-solid/
ui-svelte/
